verbose_text: Ectopic expression of rDbx1 in chick VP progenitors led to more differentiative mitoses, reducing the VZ progenitor pool over time, and increased proliferation in the SVZ because of a non-cell-autonomous effect, which must be transient because SVZ progenitors can only divide a limited number of times.
evidence: rDbx1 in chick VP progenitors led to more differentiative mitoses, reducing the VZ progenitor pool over time, and increased proliferation
